@startuml

actor Client
participant "API Gateway" as APIG
participant "Auth Middleware" as Auth
participant "Issue Service" as IssueS
participant "Database" as DB
participant "Activity Log" as AL
participant "WebSocket Server" as WS

Client -> APIG: POST /issues
APIG -> Auth: Validate JWT
Auth --> APIG: JWT valid
APIG -> IssueS: Create Issue
IssueS -> DB: Insert Issue
DB --> IssueS: Issue ID
IssueS -> AL: Log Activity
AL -> DB: Insert Log
DB --> AL: Log ID
IssueS -> WS: Broadcast New Issue
WS --> Client: Issue Created

@enduml